<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1954-05-09T06:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1954-05-09T06:00:00-05:00" n="466" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d466">
                            <note rend="inline" type="source">751G.00/5–954: Telegram</note>
                            <head><hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">United States
                                        Delegation</gloss> to the <gloss type="to">Department of
                                        State</gloss></hi></head>
                            <opener>
                                <seg rendition="#left"><hi rend="smallcaps">top secret<lb/><gloss target="#t_niact1">niact</gloss></hi></seg>
                                <dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Geneva</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1954-05-09T12:00:00+01:00">May 9,
                                    1954—noon</date>.</dateline>
                            </opener>
                            <p><gloss target="#t_Dulte1">Dulte</gloss> 56. Personal for Secretary.
                                Reference your <gloss target="#t_Tedul1">Tedul</gloss> 42.<note n="1" xml:id="d466fn1">Dated May 8, <ref target="#pg_728">p.
                                        728</ref>.</note> I put the point covered in the reference
                                paragraph of your speech to the French in a broad and unmistakable
                                hint in my private talk with <persName corresp="#p_BG1">Bidault</persName> last Friday.<note n="2" xml:id="d466fn2">Reported in telegram <gloss target="#t_Dulte1">Dulte</gloss>
                                    54, May 8, <ref target="#pg_712">p. 712</ref>.</note> He got the
                                point and it had, I think, a great deal to do with stiffening his
                                position.</p>
                            <closer><signed><persName corresp="#p_SWB1"><hi rend="smallcaps">Smith</hi></persName></signed></closer>
                        </div>
                        </body></text></TEI>